title: UFYB 70: Clean v Dirty Pain (Breakups, Death, etc)
itunes:title: Clean v Dirty Pain (Breakups, Death, etc)
description:
Discover the difference between clean and dirty pain, and how embracing this concept can diminish so much unnecessary suffering in your life. Emotional pain and misery are bound to come up, but this tool is going to help you flow through it with less resistance.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/70
